706485f-a.title: Brooklyn: Riverdale Avenue - Rockaway Avenue
706485f-a.text:
233 ang 235 Riverdale Avenue, north side, between Rockaway Avenue
and Thatford Street, showing two one-story homes, of a type not
at all common in this neighborhood. On the right is the five-story
factory of the Rockaway Wire Works.
P.L.Sperr  October 23, 1931
NO REPRODUCTIONS
